title: Ep. - 453 - JESSICA BATTEN FROM LOVE IS BLIND LOVE IS BLIND FINALE RECAP
description:
Jessica Batten from season 1 of Netflix’s Love is Blind season 2 talks about how the show changed the trajectory of her life, and this season of the show.

 

Reality Gays podcast co-hosts Matt Marr and Jake Anthony review the Love is Blind season 2 finale.
